 in relationships that may experience distrust.

864
00:34:00,240 --> 00:34:03,600
 And the reason that's interesting is

865
00:34:03,600 --> 00:34:06,300
 there's nothing untrustworthy about who God is.

866
00:34:06,300 --> 00:34:09,760
 God's the one that comes up with this idea

867
