 and yet he is not the one that runs the risk

868
00:34:13,020 --> 00:34:17,380
 of creating any distrust between he and Abram.

869
00:34:17,380 --> 00:34:22,200
 Instead, Abram is the one that poses all the risk.

870
00:34:22,200 --> 00:34:24,760
 And yet God says, hey, let's strike this thing up

871
00:34:24,760 --> 00:34:28,160
 because the reality is I will enter into it

872
00:34:28,160 --> 00:34:29,800
 though I don't need to,

873
00:34:29,800 --> 00:34:32,920
 because I want to assuage your fears,

