 though you have no reason to fear.

875
00:34:35,320 --> 00:34:38,740
 This is the compassion and kindness of God

876
00:34:38,740 --> 00:34:41,680
 towards people like you and me.

877
00:34:41,680 --> 00:34:46,420
 He sees us in our insecurity and he tells us,

