00:34:47,440 --> 00:34:52,440
 hey, that insecurity, it in no way

879
00:34:52,440 --> 00:34:57,620
 invalidates my trustworthiness,

880
00:34:57,620 --> 00:35:00,680
 but it nonetheless matters to me.

881
00:35:00,680 --> 00:35:02,040
 And so let's deal with it.

882
00:35:02,040 --> 00:35:04,160
 Let's put something in place that helps us

883
00:35:04,160 --> 00:35:07,260
 to make sure you feel safe with me.

884
00:35:07,260 --> 00:35:11,440
 And yet here's what's interesting

885
00:35:11,440 --> 00:35:13,760
 is Abram gets all this stuff together.

886
00:35:13,760 --> 00:35:16,600
 You find that time passes.

887
00:35:16,600 --> 00:35:19,780
 That's what the idea of these birds of prey

888
00:35:19,780 --> 00:35:22,240
 that Abram starts to fight off and shoo away.

889
00:35:22,240 --> 00:35:24,560
 It feels like such a weird detail.

890
00:35:24,560 --> 00:35:26,440
 And yet it speaks to us this thought

891
00:35:26,440 --> 00:35:28,480
 that he had these animals

892
00:35:28,480 --> 00:35:31,160
 and yet no action has taken place so long in fact

893
00:35:31,160 --> 00:35:33,780
 that these buzzards have come to roost.

894
00:35:33,780 --> 00:35:38,180
 And the reason nothing has happened

895
00:35:38,180 --> 00:35:40,440
 is because according to this covenant,

