00:36:02,740 --> 00:36:08,280
 Is that why you might be stalling

903
00:36:08,280 --> 00:36:10,060
 in your relationship with God?

904
00:36:10,960 --> 00:36:13,920
 Is it because you fear that if you take another step

905
00:36:13,920 --> 00:36:15,400
 with him, if you go deeper with him,

906
00:36:15,400 --> 00:36:18,360
 he's eventually gonna find out the fraud that you are,

