00:36:18,360 --> 00:36:23,020
 the failure you are, and he's gonna want out.

908
00:36:23,020 --> 00:36:24,980
 He's gonna move on.

909
00:36:24,980 --> 00:36:26,160
 He's gonna find someone better.

910
00:36:26,160 --> 00:36:28,880
 Is that the reason you're hesitant to step into

911
00:36:28,880 --> 00:36:32,540
 a relationship, a real relationship with God?

