00:37:00,320 --> 00:37:02,760
 "passed between the pieces.

921
00:37:02,760 --> 00:37:05,420
 "On that day, the Lord made a covenant with Abraham."

922
00:37:08,160 --> 00:37:10,160
 Smoking pot and a flaming torch

