00:37:15,480 --> 00:37:17,880
 All throughout the Old Testament, fire and smoke,

926
00:37:17,880 --> 00:37:21,680
 they were symbolic of his presence among his people.

927
00:37:21,680 --> 00:37:26,520
 And you see this presence of God moves through the pieces

